    <!-- FC catch-all — fires for both lifecycle events of an FC entity:
         first-time cache insert (FreeCompanyAdded) and any later persisted
         field difference (FreeCompanyChanged). Lightweight "something
         happened with this FC" line — counterpart to "Player changed (any)".
         {0} = "«TAG» Name" of the FC. -->
    <data name="ui.notifications.enrichment.freecompany_changed.label"><value>Free Company changed (general)</value></data>
    <data name="ui.notifications.enrichment.freecompany_changed.description"><value>Catch-all notification for every kind in the "Free Company history" group — fires both when an FC is first added to the cache and when any persisted field changes later (name, tag, active member count, slogan, focus flags, …). Lightweight roll-up — turn this off if you've enabled the granular per-kind notifications below to avoid duplicate lines.</value></data>
    <data name="ui.notifications.enrichment.freecompany_changed.format"><value>Free Company {0} has changed</value></data>

    <!-- First-time persistence of an FC entity in nexus_external_free_company —
         fires exactly once when an FC upsert produced a brand-new row (never
         seen in cache before). {0} = "«TAG» Name" of the FC. -->
    <data name="ui.notifications.enrichment.freecompany_added.label"><value>Free Company added</value></data>
